nohz: Align periodic tick Kconfig with other choices' naming convention

Rename CONFIG_PERIODIC_HZ to CONFIG_HZ_PERIODIC in
order to stay consistent with other tick implementation
entries:

	CONFIG_HZ_PERIODIC
	CONFIG_NO_HZ_IDLE
	CONFIG_NO_HZ_FULL

